title: Zaahirah
subTitle: Full Stack Website Dev
intro: The project aims to create a comprehensive and user-friendly travel website using the React framework for the frontend, Node.js for the backend, and MySQL as the database management system.
body: The website will serve as a platform for users to explore and book various travel services offered by Zaahira Travels.
conclusion: The use of React for the frontend, Node.js for the backend, and MySQL for the database ensures a robust and scalable solution. The seamless integration of various features and secure payment options will provide an enhanced user experience.
